@howard0su  thx! I follow your solutions and find just copy libopenblas.*, still meet errors. Then I decide to set LD_LIBRARY_PATH in .bashrc file to add openblas and opencv. then source the file to make it work.
the set: export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=${LD_LIBRARY_PATH}:/usr/local/lib64:/opt/openblas/lib:/data/apps/opencv-2.4.13/release/lib

now I can import mxnet successfully. I will check it can run well.

@glingyan 

Thanks for your explain.
I will wait for windows version since I do my dialy work on windows (this is why I use mxnet :))

